<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chanchin Pha dakte a giu, Gamtin leh tuipi chungah;
 Hukdamna manbei kipah um, Nang leh kei ei hun tun ui;
 Pathien khawvel hehpih, A Chapa neihsun A piei;
 Amah gingcha taphawtte chun,
 Kumsawt hinna changun au.

[V2]
 Chanchin pha dak a giu,
 Gamtin leh tuipi chung ah;
 Chanchin pha'n a hun tun,
 Nang leh kei di'n vangsak na.

[V3]
 2. Chanchin Pha dakin ei chiel, Mitin guolvakna di'n;
 Chielna ngaihsak loin um ki'n, Hehpih sapna chu niel ki'n;
 &quot;Hinna Changthak Ka hi, Thagau a gilkiel te An;
 Na gitloh sandup bang mahleh,
 Vuk bangin hung vam ina&quot;!

[V4]
 3. Chanchin Pha dak vau lawkna, Nichengin a hung gi zel;
 A vaigei taphawtte dinga, Thihna lauhum hung tung ding;
 &quot;Na hinna di'n taidawk in, Phaicham ale kichawl ki'n&quot;
 Na nunglam nga kit hiel kinla,
 Kumsawt gawtna thuok kha'n la.

[V5]
 4. Chanchin Pha dak kipahum, Gamtin, muntin, a thawng hi;
 Ngaihdamnabukim thuchuhpuo'n, KhetdenHukdampaziekchun;
 &quot;Chanchin Pha kipahum, Micheng dingin ka hun puoi;
 Nanguh di'n Hukdampa a pieng,
 Krista Lal, Lalpen chuh.&quot;</lyrics>
<title>THE GOSPEL BELLS</title>
<hymn_number>263</hymn_number>
</song>